<plot>Welcome to the Chop Shop, the anti-hair salon with a permanent sneer and a heart of gold. This fun, cutting-edge docusoap follows bad-boy hair salon owner Danile Hudon and his motley crew of punk rock stylists as they get into each other's hair everyday. This counter-culture group forms a tight, rock &amp; roll family who work fight and party hard under the same roof while delivering wicked style to their clients at Daniel's one-of-a-kind hair salon in Vancouver - the Chop Shop.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?104476</url></doc>
